HEADWORD: Externalize
<hw>Ex*ter"nal*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To make
external; to manifest by outward form.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Thought <qex>externalizes</qex> itself in language.</q>
<rj><qau>Soyce.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Externally</ent>⟦br⟧
